'''Anti-personnel missiles''' were used by the [[Aargau Home Guard]]. During the Guard's military exercise display, [[Darth Vader's valet]] attempted to telekinetically guide such a missile to kill Viscount [[Tardi]]. However, [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] projected a [[Hologram/Legends|hologram]] of Tardi over the valet, and one of the valet over Tardi, causing the valet to direct the missile to kill himself.

